SUMMARY:Lambda Node.js 20 Phase 1
DESCRIPTION:Lambda functions using Node.js 20 runtime will fail to update. Phase 1: CreateFunction and UpdateFunctionConfiguration blocked. Source: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/lambda/latest/dg/lambda-runtimes.html
URL:https://docs.aws.amazon.com/lambda/latest/dg/lambda-runtimes.html
END:VEVENT
